### 1. Ingest
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ingest
{
    "vehicleId": "tesla-model3-2025-long-range",
    "year": 2025,
    ... }

### 2. Ask about one vehicle
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/tesla-model3-2025-long-range/ask

{
 "question": "What is the horsepower and drivetrain?",
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}


### 3. Fleet search across all vehicles
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask

{
    "question": "Which vehicles have over 400 horsepower?",
    "topK": 5
}